END_PGML_HINT
############################################################ # Solution ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION In the second quadrant, the vector field flows in the opposite direction, and in the first quadrant it flows in the same direction as the curve. Notice however that the amount of flow in each quadrant (positive and negative) are roughly equal, so the integral is zero.
END_PGML_SOLUTION
############################################################ # End Problem ############################################################
ENDDOCUMENT();

setup.pg-code:
$MC1= PopUp(
["?","positive.","negative.","zero.","there is not enough information to decide."],
"negative." # correct answer
);

